      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-31/nycb-not-a-community-bank-issue-ex-fed-governor-duke-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前美联储理事贝齐·杜克 (Betsy Duke) 对纽约社区银行 (New York Community Bancorp) 股价暴跌发表评论，原因是投资者担心商业房地产风险。]]></description>
